title: Fabbri gets tiebreaker in 3rd as Blues beat Oilers, McDavid
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
Rookie Robby Fabbri scored the tiebreaking goal midway through the third period to help the St. Louis Blues beat Edmonton 3-1 Thursday night...
